snippet: Japan will seek to avenge a loss to the United Arab Emirates when they travel to face the West Asian side at the resumption of the final round of regional World Cup qualifying in March, coach Vahid Halilhodzic said....
lead_paragraph: Japan will seek to avenge a loss to the United Arab Emirates when they travel to face the West Asian side at the resumption of the final round of regional World Cup qualifying in March, coach Vahid Halilhodzic said.

headline.main: Halilhodzic Eager for Japan to Exact Revenge Over UAE
headline.print_headline: Halilhodzic Eager for Japan to Exact Revenge Over UAE
